{"tid":2261763,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"中籍韓團成員發文慶「抗美援朝」 韓國民眾氣炸請願政府制裁","createTime":"2020-10-28T14:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T15:44:56.000Z","uid":74065,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"306e2ea08d4ececa32193c6377f07bbbe24543cb","tid":2261763,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/10/28/phpJWYHcu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F10%2F28%2FphpJWYHcu.png&h=4ad56a41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓網友在官方請願網站發起連署，要求政府制裁公開支持「抗美援朝」的中國籍韓團成員。（圖擷自「青瓦台請願」網站）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕南韓偶像天團「BTS防彈少年團」在7日因「促進美韓關係」獲得「符立德獎」（James A. Van Fleet Award），剛好今年是「韓戰70周年」，團員以此作為得獎感言，勿忘2國的犧牲者，讓中國粉絲氣炸。近期中國高調宣傳「抗美援朝」，多名中國籍韓團成員在微博上紀念抗戰英雄，引爆韓國網友怒火，痛斥這些人在韓國累積足夠知名度才有今天的成就，卻公開支持被扭曲的歷史，紛紛請願要求政府禁止他們到韓國活動。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，「BTS防彈少年團」月初因得獎感言，得罪中國愛國小粉絲，慘被砲轟「無視中國抗戰烈士的犧牲」，引發南韓民眾不滿，又因中國官方23日高調慶祝「抗美援朝勝利」，稱中國和北韓成功抵禦「美國帝國主義的擴張」，扭曲北韓侵略南韓事實，並將韓戰視為「中朝正義戰爭」，讓南韓人民氣炸。<br />\n<br />\n而同日，中國官方在微博上發起「紀念志願軍抗美援朝紀念作戰70周年」活動，韓團出身的偶像EXO成員張藝興、f（x）隊長宋茜、宇宙少女成員程瀟、還有已解散的I.O.I成員周潔瓊均轉發貼文「向英雄致敬」，讓南韓網友忍無可忍，痛罵這群人是在韓國出道累積人氣後才有如此成就，他們卻公開支持被扭曲的歷史，還視韓戰中侵略南韓的中國士兵為英雄，讓網友怒在青瓦台請願上發起連署，要政府「不要再讓這些中國成員繼續在韓國活動」，短短2天已有超過2萬人響應。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/10/28/php6TLCmr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F10%2F28%2Fphp6TLCmr.jpg&h=85de3425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓團EXO成員張藝興、f（x）隊長宋茜在微博上向「抗美援朝」英雄致敬。（圖擷自微博）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/10/28/phpTJhVRH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F10%2F28%2FphpTJhVRH.jpg&h=1c1f939d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宇宙少女成員程瀟、還有已解散的I.O.I成員周潔瓊在微博上向「抗美援朝」英雄致敬。（圖擷自微博）"},{"pid":"bead438be8f25912f77db075ad3ecb1b9be38f9e","tid":2261763,"uid":222155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfeb4bb958f41a9e7cea96f6a4ce9dd26112f10","tid":2261763,"uid":205928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T15:10:54.000Z","msg":"好波！"},{"pid":"34aeb3af738b9408cfee722c269e5077c1c4d44f","tid":2261763,"uid":253373,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T15:14:45.000Z","msg":"呢4條友都搬返大陸搵食，唔會去韓國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n制裁D仲喺韓國活動既好過"},{"pid":"a2d18b51d74b84c09ff6f23aac15e6f90d8b2e1a","tid":2261763,"uid":2781,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T15:38:55.000Z","msg":"直頭咪俾呢幾條友入境"},{"pid":"ae71b76684cede127925f8285a69a1e2d270e077","tid":2261763,"uid":148262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T15:44:56.000Z","msg":"成日覺得韓國啲娛樂公司好親共 好鍾意rmb<br />\n個政府都好似打算同中国fd啲咁<br />\n唔覺會做到啲乜"}]}